By Andile Mngxitama BIG QUESTION: Cuba and China are not in South Africa (SA) to help us with this coronavirus that they have defeated – why? ANSWER: If they come here Stellenbosch, Bill Gates and the CR17 donors won’t make profits out of our deaths and sicknesses. This explains why there is no shutdown and President Ramaphosa is taking his time. The government needs 70% of the population to get infected. #ShutDownSA Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization.